msgid ""
"Maintaining security on your system is extremely important, and one approach "
"for this task is to manage access to system services carefully. Your system "
"may need to provide open access to particular services (for example, "
"<command>httpd</command> if you are running a Web server). However, if you do "
"not need to provide a service, you should turn it off to minimize your "
"exposure to possible bug exploits."
msgstr ""
"És extremadament important mantenir segur el vostre sistema, i una manera "
"d'aconseguir-ho és gestionar cuidadosament els accessos als serveis del "
"sistema. El vostre sistema podria necessitar mantenir accessos a serveis "
"particulars (per exemple, l'<command>httpd</command> si esteu executant un "
"servidor web). No obstant, si no necessiteu donar un cert servei, l'haurieu "
"de desactivar per minimitzar la vostra exposició a possibles atacs."

#: /home/nils/src/system-config-services/hosted/doc/C/system-config-services-complete.xml:44(para)
#: /home/nils/src/system-config-services/hosted/doc/C/system-config-services-complete.xml:63(para)
msgid ""
"There are several different methods for managing access to system services. "
"Choose which method of management to use based on the service, your system's "
"configuration, and your level of Linux expertise."
msgstr ""
"Hi ha diversos mètodes per gestionar l'accés als serveis del sistema. "
"Escolliu quin mètode de gestió a utilitzar basat en el servei, la vostra "
"configuració del sistema i el vostre nivell de coneixements del Linux."

#: /home/nils/src/system-config-services/hosted/doc/C/system-config-services-complete.xml:47(para)
#: /home/nils/src/system-config-services/hosted/doc/C/system-config-services-complete.xml:66(para)
msgid ""
"The easiest way to deny access to a service is to turn it off. Both the "
"services managed by <command>xinetd</command> and the services in the "
"<filename>/etc/rc.d/init.d</filename> hierarchy (also known as SysV services) "
"can be configured to start or stop with the <application>Services "
"Configuration Tool</application>."
msgstr ""
"La forma més facil de denegar l'accés a un servei es desactivar-lo. Tant els "
"serveis gestionats per <command>xinetd</command> com els serveis de la "
"jerarquia <filename>/etc/rc.d/init.d</filename> (també coneguts com serveis "
"SysV) poden ser configurats per iniciar-se o aturar-se amb "
"l'<application>Eina de configuració de serveis</application>."

